le=\"博士后管理\">博士后管理</a></li>\n           <li><a href=\"../../kxyj/zcpt.htm\" title=\"支撑平台\">支撑平台</a></li>\n          </ul>\n      </li>\n\n    \n    <li>  <a href=\"javascript:;\">人才培养</a>\n          <ul>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rcpy/bksjy/xkgk.htm\" title=\"本科生教育\">本科生教育</a></li>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rcpy/yjsjy/xkgk.htm\" title=\"研究生教育\">研究生教育</a></li>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rcpy/xsgz/xgxtjj.htm\" title=\"学生工作\">学生工作</a></li>\n          </ul>\n      </li>\n\n    \n    <li>  <a href=\"javascript:;\">人才招聘</a>\n          <ul>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rczp/jszp.htm\" title=\"教师招聘\">教师招聘</a></li>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rczp/bshzp.htm\" title=\"博士后招聘\">博士后招聘</a></li>\n           <li><a href=\"../../rczp/qtzp.htm\" title=\"其他招聘\">其他招聘</a></li>\n          </ul>\n      </li>\n\n</ul></div>\n\n\n\n\n </div></div>\n<!--header-->\n<div class=\"content\">\n <div class=\"banner faculty\">\n  <div class=\"mainWrap relative\">\n    <div class=\"channelname\"><b></b>\n\n\n\n师资队伍</div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"local\"><div class=\"mainWrap\"><i class=\"icon-home\"></i> <a href=\"\">&nbsp;\n                        </a><a href=\"../../index.htm\" class=\"navigation_style\">首页</a>\n                <span>&gt;</span> \n                <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navigation_style\">师资队伍</a>\n                <span>&gt;</span> \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jzyg1.htm\" class=\"navigation_style\">教职员工</a>\n                <span>&gt;</span> \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jzyg1/jxxl.htm\" class=\"navigation_style\">教学系列</a>\n</div></div>\n <div class=\"mainWrap\">\n  \n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"innercontent\">\n\n        <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"szcontent\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div class=\"facultydetail clearfix contbtmpd\">\n <div class=\"img\">\n  <img src=\"/__local/7/46/15/8A87B97A4AD68FF5D230DD83FCD_8EF08539_61E04.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/746158A87B97A4AD68FF5D230DD83FCD/8EF08539/61E04\" vheight=\" 291px\" vwidth=\" 200px\" width=\"200\" height=\"291\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" orisrc=\"/__local/7/46/15/8A87B97A4AD68FF5D230DD83FCD_8EF08539_61E04.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\" style=\"width: 200px; height: 291px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;\n </div>\n <div class=\"article\">\n  <h1>王田 博士</h1>\n  <h2>讲师</h2>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>2010.08-2014.07／清华大学／学士</p>\n  <p>2014.09-2020.03／加利福尼亚大学圣地亚哥校区／博士</p>\n  <p>2020.03-2020.08／美国索尔克研究所／博士后</p>\n  <p>2020.09-至今／清华大学生命科学学院／讲师</p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <h2>● &nbsp;研究兴趣、领域：</h2>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>能量稳态的维持，对于生物体的生存是必需的。生活在自然界的动物，需要随时应对变化的外界环境，进行合理的能量分配，以最大化生存几率。当面对外界压力时，动物体内的代谢过程会发生变化；转录因子通过调控基因表达，调节代谢过程。我们利用分子生物学，遗传学，生物化学和生物信息学等方法，研究转录因子和共转录因子在压力环境下，对机体代谢的调节机制。<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <h2 style=\"white-space: normal;\">● &nbsp;开设课程：</h2>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>《遗传学》（全英文授课），本科生专业必修课</p>\n  <p>《生物钟与健康》，本科生通识选修课</p>\n  <p>《生物化学基础实验》，本科生专业必修课</p>\n  <p>《生物化学与分子生物学综合实验》</p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <h2>● &nbsp;代表性论文：</h2>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\">1. <strong>Wang T</strong>, Wiater E, Zhang X, Thomas JB, Montminy M. Crtc modulates fasting programs associated with 1-C metabolism and inhibition of insulin signaling. Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A. 2021 Mar 23;118(12):e2024865118.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\">2. WANG Zhipeng, <strong>WANG Tian</strong>, MA Xinyu, ZHANG Jun. (2017). Rethink of the native base structures, base pairing, and functions through non-natural bases. Chemistry of Life, 37(6), 946-951.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\">3. Zhi-Peng, W., Chen-Chen, C., <strong>Tian, W.</strong>, Miao, W., &amp; Yi-Ming, L. (2014). The Progress in Phosphohistidine Research. Progress in Biochemistry and Biophysics, 41(5), 413-424.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\">4. Lu, B., Shao, L., Feng, S., <strong>Wang, T.</strong>, &amp; Zhong, Y. (2014). The β-alanyl-monoamine synthase ebony is regulated by schizophrenia susceptibility gene dysbindin in Drosophila. Science China Life Sciences, 57(1), 46-51.</p>\n  <p>&nbsp;<br></p>\n  <h2>● &nbsp;荣誉、奖励及参加学术团体的情况：</h2>\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\n  <p>2012-2014 Member of Tsinghua Xuetang Talent Program</p>\n  <p>2018-2020 Vice President of Tsinghua Alumni Association at San Diego</p>\n  <p>2019-2020 Chapman Scholar, The Mary K. Chapman Foundation</p>\n  <p>2020 第九届清华大学青年教师教学大赛理科及医科组 一等奖</p>\n  <p>2021 北京高校第十二届青年教师教学基本功比赛理科A组 三等奖</p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <h2>● &nbsp;联系方式：</h2>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p>邮箱: &nbsp;wangtian@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn<br>通讯地址：清华大学生命科学学院</p>\n </div>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    \n</div>\n</form>\n\n </div>\n</div>\n<!--footer-->\n<div class=\"footer\">\n<div class=\"section_1\">\n  <div class=\"mainWrap relative\">\n  <b></b>\n\n<div class=\"ewmright\">            <img src=\"../../images/shengming20221011.jpg\" border=\"0\"> <p style=\"font-size: 14px;    line-height: 1.5em;color: #fff;\"> 欢迎关注清华生命学院公众号</p>\n</div>\n\n   <div class=\"right\"><h2>人才招聘</h2> \n<ul class=\"jobslist\">\n    <li><a href=\"../../rczp/jszp.htm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1662533482, 67174)\"> <i class=\"icon-angle-right\"></i> 教师招聘</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../rczp/bshzp.htm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1662533482, 67175)\"> <i class=\"icon-angle-right\"></i> 博士后招聘</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../rc